OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day for many with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine, although low cloud may
OL,7,Faffect areas near to the coast at
OL,8,Ftimes. Sunshine may also turn a little
OL,9,Fhazy elsewhere throughout the
OL,10,Fafternoon, but feeling very warm for
OL,11,Fmost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining fine initially this
OL,14,Fevening, but cloud will spread in from
OL,15,Fthe west. Overnight some spots of rain
OL,16,Fare possible but most remaining dry. A
OL,17,Fmild night for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
