OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAny early cloud retreating
OL,6,Fback to western coasts giving way to a
OL,7,Fdry and sunny day for most. Feeling
OL,8,Fvery warm in the sunshine, although a
OL,9,Flittle fresher near coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FRemaining dry and settled throughout
OL,13,FSunday and early next week with plenty
OL,14,Fof sunshine. Feeling very warm or hot
OL,15,Fby day with potentially some warm
OL,16,Fnights too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
